This position reports to the IT Executive and communicates with various departments. The trainees will be involved in full web development cycle from website creation, execution, development, maintenance to performing campaign activities


Trainees will be involved in
1. Creation and maintenance of e-commerce website
2. Developing and managing digital contents
3. Generating clear and attractive website content (products, content, promotions)
4. Coordination and execution for digital campaigns, sales events and promotions
Corresponding with customers on their enquiries and feedback.